<sec id="conclusion-and-future-work">
  <title>Conclusion and Future Work</title>
  <p>We present the features of the TorchGAN framework and demonstrate
  its extensibility, ease of use and efficiency. Future work and
  extensions under active development include, integration of GAN models
  for video generation, generalization of the training loop to support
  Inference GAN models, such that they can be conveniently modified and
  extended, addition of features such as Adaptive Instance Normalization
  layers, and expanding the model zoo and documentation to cover more
  sophisticated examples such as Multi Agent-GAN training. We also
  envision the extension of the framework to domains beyond Computer
  Vision by adding support for NLP and Time Series GAN models.</p>
</sec>
